119cbdee56006b9cad1de497b810447a05aa7f7f.query:
UPDATE
                 notification
               SET
                 status = $1
               WHERE
                 NOT source_id = ANY($2)
                 AND (status = 'Read' OR status = 'Unread')
               RETURNING
                 id,
                 title,
                 kind,
                 status,
                 source_id,
                 metadata as "metadata: Json<GithubNotification>",
                 updated_at,
                 last_read_at

30b90d11d290029f0f53355b764fe1a1d1b6c541.query:
INSERT INTO notification
            (id, title, kind, status, source_id, metadata, updated_at, last_read_at)
          VALUES
            ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8)

535272cb961b9d23b12c81ef8cbd5cb2f923f5ce.query:
INSERT INTO notification
            (id, title, kind, status, source_id, metadata, updated_at, last_read_at)
          VALUES
            ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8)
          ON CONFLICT (source_id) DO UPDATE
          SET
            title = $2,
            kind = $3,
            status = $4,
            metadata = $6,
            updated_at = $7,
            last_read_at = $8
          RETURNING
            id

594d8f69de74f3c64464193afbbe7dc47661a9bf.query:
SELECT
                 id,
                 title,
                 kind,
                 status,
                 source_id,
                 metadata as "metadata: Json<GithubNotification>",
                 updated_at,
                 last_read_at
               FROM notification
               WHERE id = $1
